dct_description_sm: Ustredni Sprava Geodezie a Karrtgografie. Selected buildings are shown pictorially. Insets: north continued map to Horni Lomany; regional map showing main thoroughfares. Published in cooperation with Ceskoslovenske Statni Lazne = [Czechoslovakian Public Baths]. Verso: Index to spas, hotels, and tourist ammenities. 1962
